| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0539 — Recovery Inhibition (ElDorado)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 883555e8-ef54-5456-b977-5310f764ae66"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
